{
  "stem": "21437.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, you know, occasionally we got a little bit of cheese.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not really-- occasionally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or a little bit of margarine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most of the time it was just, you know-- whoever came-- whoever you happen to have-- if whoever was standing there mixed it through, so you got a bit, you know-- if you got from the bottom of it, pardon the expression, but it was a bit thicker.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise there could have been kohlrabis or a few-- or some rotten potato or whatever it was that they couldn't use anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They dished it out to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All along the roll calls and the-- the-- the shouting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All along.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was part and parcel of it, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were-- at that stage, I think that was already after years of this kind of a verbal and physical abuse, that you just, you know-- If I could describe-- if I could paint it for you, I could, but you really-- you know, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you were just hanging in there, really, by the skin of your teeth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nothing else for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why one survived and the other one-- I-- I believe that every survivor's a walking and talking miracle because that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because now it was-- no, by that time I already met other people, you see, I-- And somehow-- I-- I am very lucky this way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if I happened to be lucky to that I meet such people, or maybe they recognized something in me that we respond to each other.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I think it was happening to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Put it this way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have any other choices.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
